Description:
You arrive at a small camp on the shore and there you see an elven priest fishing, when you approach he tells you.

"Hello travellers, when the city froze I was here fishing... I was lucky,... but now I can't do much more....

I am not strong enough to help the frozen elves in the city, but at least I can help you if you need me to heal your injuries.
DescriptionAction: Or else, you can also fish with me. Although in these icy waters there are not many fish left."
